      <td width="50%" valign="middle" align="center"><!--mstheme--><font face="book antiqua,times new roman,times">
        <p align="center"><strong>The Hilgard House
        Hotel &amp; Suites is a modern European style hotel located at the
        southern edge of the UCLA campus in the heart of Westwood Village.
        Hilgard House is the <i><u>museum</u></i> hotel, within walking distance
        of the Armand Hammer and
        Fowler museums, and just 10 minutes by car from the new Getty
        Center.&nbsp; Beaches, shopping, business, cultural and entertainment
        centers are minutes away.</strong></p>
      <!--mstheme--></font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width="50%" valign="middle" align="center"><!--mstheme--><font face="book antiqua,times new roman,times"><strong>Room rates are
        $154.00
        plus tax for one person to $159.00 plus tax for two people. Special
        rates are available during some periods. All rates include free parking
        and a complimentary continental breakfast.</strong>
        <p><strong><font color="#CC0066">Ask us about special rates
        for finding us on the Internet when you are making your reservations -
        or check out our <a href="reservationsform.htm"> Reservations Request Form</a> for the special
        rates.</font></strong></p>
		<p><strong>Within a few blocks of hotel, Westwood
        Village offers shops, theaters and more than seventy restaurants with a wide variety of
        cuisine.</strong></p>
